-x-ANDOR_R
en
conf t
license boot module c2900 technology-package securityk9
yes
do wr
do reload

en
conf t
hostname ANDOR_R
zone security INSIDE
exit
zone security OUTSIDE
exit
int gig0/3/0
description Az ISP területe és a Projectenis telephelyei felé. / Towards the site of the ISP and towards the sites of PRJCTNS.
ip add 80.90.125.37 255.255.255.252
ip nat outside
zone-member security OUTSIDE
no sh
exit
int gig0/1.3
description Az ANDOR első emeleti VLAN-hoz fenn tartott al-interface. / The first floor VLAN subinterface of ANDOR site.
encapsulation dot1q 3
ip add 172.16.15.1 255.255.255.192
ip helper-address 80.90.125.33
ip nat inside
no sh
exit
int gig0/1.6
description Az ANDOR második emeleti VLAN-hoz fenn tartott al-interface. / The second floor VLAN subinterface of ANDOR site.
encapsulation dot1q 6
ip add 172.16.15.65 255.255.255.192
ip helper-address 80.90.125.33
ip nat inside
no sh
exit
int gig0/1.9
description Az ANDOR földszinti VLAN-hoz fenn tartott al-interface. / The ground floor VLAN subinterface of ANDOR site.
encapsulation dot1q 9
ip add 172.16.15.129 255.255.255.224
ip helper-address 80.90.125.33
ip nat inside
no sh
exit
int gig0/1.12
description Az ANDOR adminisztratív VLAN alhálózatának fenn tartott al-interface. / The administrative VLAN subnetworks subinterface of ANDOR.
encapsulation dot1q 12 native
ip add 172.16.15.161 255.255.255.240
ip nat inside
no sh
exit
int gig0/1
ip nat inside
zone-member security INSIDE
no sh
exit
router ospf 1
router-id 7.7.7.7
Network 172.16.15.0 0.0.0.63 area 2
Network 172.16.15.64 0.0.0.63 area 2
Network 172.16.15.128 0.0.0.31 area 2
Network 172.16.15.160 0.0.0.15 area 2
Network 80.90.125.36 0.0.0.3 area 0
passive-interface gig0/1.3
passive-interface gig0/1.6
passive-interface gig0/1.9
passive-interface gig0/1.12
passive-interface gig0/1
exit
ip domain-name Projectenis.com
enable pass wasp67
user Overlord839 password ibmadmin839
user IBMadmin999 password 9rutk9skac9
user Rocket375 password projectenis375
user Rifle622 password projectenis622
user Andoradmin password andoradmin34
crypto key generate rsa
1024

ip ssh version 2
ip ssh authentication-retries 2
ip ssh time-out 120
line vty 0 15
transport input ssh
login local
exit
banner motd %This device is only accesable by registered authorized personnel within work hours. Accessing the device unregurarly, or any tampering that damages the owners and the comapny, will result in legal action being taken.%

class-map type inspect match-any ALLOWED-TRAFFIC
match protocol dns
match protocol http
match protocol https
exit
policy-map type inspect INSIDE-POLICY
class type inspect ALLOWED-TRAFFIC
inspect
class class-default
drop
exit
zone-pair security INSIDE-TO-OUTSIDE source INSIDE destination OUTSIDE
service-policy type inspect INSIDE-POLICY
exit
int g0/1
zone-member security INSIDE
exit
int g0/3/0
zone-member security OUTSIDE
exit
do wr



